{
  "ref": "brewer",
  "categoryRef": "npc",
  "title": "Brewer",
  "sections": [
    {
      "title": "Standard dialogue after Rum Deal",
      "sections": [
        {
          "title": "Brewer 1",
          "sections": [],
          "dialogues": [
            {
              "lines": [
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "Hello there!"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Brewer",
                  "text": "You saved us! Huzzah!"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "All in a day's work, think nothing of it."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Brewer",
                  "text": "I don't have anything to reward you with except my collection of bleak, gothic poetry I wrote when I assumed we were all done for. Do you want it?"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "I may come for it later, you hang on to it for now."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "title": "Brewer 2",
          "sections": [],
          "dialogues": [
            {
              "lines": [
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "Hello there!"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Brewer",
                  "text": "I don't know what your game is, but I know you're one of THEM!"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "But I just saved you!"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Brewer",
                  "text": "The voices tell me different. It's all part of a plot! Confess!"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "title": "Brewer 3",
          "sections": [],
          "dialogues": [
            {
              "lines": [
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "Hello there!"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Brewer",
                  "text": "Have they gone yet?"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "Well, no, but they are a lot calmer now."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Brewer",
                  "text": "What are we gonna do now, huh? What are we gunna do now?"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "In your case I would say relax."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "title": "Brewer 4",
          "sections": [],
          "dialogues": [
            {
              "lines": [
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "Hello there!"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Brewer",
                  "text": "Well you proved that you're probably not a zombie."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Brewer",
                  "text": "So what are you then? A ghoul? A vampyre?"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "I'm not any form of undead!"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Brewer",
                  "text": "Oh...oh god I'm sorry, I didn't realise it was natural..."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "What?"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Brewer",
                  "text": "Nothing..."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "title": "Brewer 5",
          "sections": [],
          "dialogues": [
            {
              "lines": [
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "Hello there!"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Brewer",
                  "text": "Hello there, brave hero, in whom I had total confidence!"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "Total confidence?"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Brewer",
                  "text": "Yes! I was so confident that I would never, ever have sold your soft, edible body to the pirates outside!"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "Well, great..."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Brewer",
                  "text": "On a completely unrelated note, I would steer clear of Hungry Frank for a while."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Brewer",
                  "text": "He's a filthy liar. And a forger. It wouldn't surprise me if he has written out a note detailing the terms of our surrender and your dismemberment and cooking in MY handwriting."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Brewer",
                  "text": "Imagine that, the fiend."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "title": "Brewer 6",
          "sections": [],
          "dialogues": [
            {
              "lines": [
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "So...got any sleep yet?"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Brewer",
                  "text": "My brain is no longer capable of sleep."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "So...what are you going to do now?"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Brewer",
                  "text": "I was gonna try and will myself dead."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "Right...good luck with that."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "title": "Brewer 7",
          "sections": [],
          "dialogues": [
            {
              "lines": [
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "Hello there!"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Brewer",
                  "text": "Hello yerself Landlubber!"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "Everything ok with you now?"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Brewer",
                  "text": "Hmmm...Overall everything is good!"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "Great!"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "title": "Brewer 8",
          "sections": [],
          "dialogues": [
            {
              "lines": [
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "Hello there!"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Brewer",
                  "text": "Hello yourself!"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "How's things?"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Brewer",
                  "text": "Fine..."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "Excellent! Since I get the feeling I don't want to know why you said that so oddly I'll just go over here!"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Brewer",
                  "text": "I think that would be for the best!"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "dialogues": []
    }
  ]
}